title: Pennsylvania Department of Health, Intermediate Care Facilities, Pennsylvania, 2007
name: Pennsylvania Department of Health, Intermediate Care Facilities, Pennsylvania, 2007
description:
Abstract:

    PA Intermediate care facilities from the Department of Health's quality assurance database.  Current as of 10/29/2007.

    Purpose:

    This layer was developed for use in emergency situations and for the general public.

    Supplemental_Information:

    The intermediate care facility addresses were geocoded.  Geocoding of addresses creates points of estimated locations.  These locations were not verified.  The user should assume that there is some spacial error.
